 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 13, "score_up": 29, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZMMLF14", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 74, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8553496, "raw_content": "Having had the good fortune of attending a practice round and first round in years past, I can attest to how incredibly nice and classy it is.\n\nAugusta puts on an absolutely perfect event, especially for the patrons.\n\nYou will not hear any disrespectful insults or shouts from the crowd.  Every single patron is absolutely courteous.  You can set up a chair in a viewing area and if you leave to go to the bathroom or get food, you will come back to your empty chair.  No one will take it.\n\nThe Masters in as close to utopia as it gets.\n\nThe members are all around the course throughout the day.  A member will not leave the clubhouse without their green jacket on.  \n\nThere are multiple food lines and very nice young ladies are there to direct and assist.  The lines move through super fast.  Food is really inexpensive.  Gift shop is expensive but food and drink are not.  They also do not charge for parking.\n", "author": "dataonly", "created": 1776002841385, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "TrancePhreak", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "If You Want to See How Nice America Can Be, Watch the Masters Today", "last_comment_created": 1776024048255, "content": "<p>Having had the good fortune of attending a practice round and first round in years past, I can attest to how incredibly nice and classy it is.</p>\n<p>Augusta puts on an absolutely perfect event, especially for the patrons.</p>\n<p>You will not hear any disrespectful insults or shouts from the crowd.  Every single patron is absolutely courteous.  You can set up a chair in a viewing area and if you leave to go to the bathroom or get food, you will come back to your empty chair.  No one will take it.</p>\n<p>The Masters in as close to utopia as it gets.</p>\n<p>The members are all around the course throughout the day.  A member will not leave the clubhouse without their green jacket on.</p>\n<p>There are multiple food lines and very nice young ladies are there to direct and assist.  The lines move through super fast.  Food is really inexpensive.  Gift shop is expensive but food and drink are not.  They also do not charge for parking.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 22, "score_up": 74, "is_edited": true, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2043059012556722506", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZMMLVnd", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 66, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8553559, "raw_content": "", "author": "k-doe3", "created": 1776005069209, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Bornhere", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZMMLVnd.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/iamufohunter/status/2043059012556722506", "author_flair_class": 